Lab #7 - CSRF where Referer validation depends on header being present
Vulnerable parameter - email change functionality
Goal - exploit the csrf vulnerability and change the email address
Creds - wiener:peter 

Analysis:
In order for a csrf attack to be possible:
#- A relevant action - change a user email - Satisfied
#- Cookie based session handling - session cookie - Satisfied
#- No unpredictable request parameters - no csrf token (Satisfied)